OL,7,FA father whose family were forced to
OL,8,Fstay with relatives after being left
OL,9,Fwithout heating for five days says the
OL,10,Fwater company blamed for the disruption
OL,11,Fshould be "held to account".
OL,13,FJames Burdett, 46, lives in one of
OL,14,Faround 2,000 homes in the Sheffield
OL,15,Fsuburb of Stannington which were left
OL,16,Fwithout central heating after a
OL,17,FYorkshire Water main burst on Friday,
OL,18,Fsending hundreds of thousands of litres
OL,19,Fof water flooding into the gas network.
OL,3,CYorkshire Water sparks fury after gas
OL,4,Cflood left family with no heating for
OL,5,Cfive days
